  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>A fetal creature of bone grows inside, its delicate body suspended in vitellus. Its fleshless limbs are comprised of soft cartilage, which will harden and densify as it grows. <br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be <span class=\"name name-special\">skeletal</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">elephantine</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一颗活生生的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>一个由骨骼构成的生物幼体正在里面成长，卵黄包裹着它脆弱的身体。它没有血肉的肢体完全由软骨构成，随着它逐渐成长，这些软骨将会逐渐硬化并变得愈发密实。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-special\">骨骼</span>以及<span class=\"name name-stellar\">庞大</span>的基因潜质。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">即將孵化！</span><br><br>蛋裡面有個骨頭胚胎，脆弱的身體懸在卵黃中。缺少肌膚的肢體由軟骨構成，未來會隨著成長逐漸變硬、密度變高。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下特徵：<span class=\"name name-special\">骨感</span>及<span class=\"name name-stellar\">體型龐大</span>。"
  },
